{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story12","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":402301}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Is this the future world...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402301},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402601}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"It looks like it hasn't changed since the last time@we were here."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Where is...Sakurako...?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Let's check the outside too!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yes..."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"bg":"bg_adv_19131.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story17","chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":400},{"id":831303,"motion":400}],"nameCenter":"Kagome & Torte","textCenter":"[chara:102001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][chara:831303:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"The city...is gone?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"And there's...a red moon in the sky."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_24015.jpg","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"autoTurnLast":3.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_19131.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Calm down, let's explore the surroundings a bit.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"Right."},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"There are no roads, and I can't@see any lights from town...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Yes, there's no trace of human habitation at all."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Have humans...perished?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"It seems so."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Without the existence of La Pucelle@and with Isabeau's power expanding,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Everything would lead to the collapse of human@civilization."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"But what about that room we were in?@Who created it?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"The original world hasn't been completely eroded@yet,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"so it's still there."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"The existence of Kagome Satori and that building@are unaffected by the changes in the world."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"This place might have become a special point."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...What about Crescent House?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Let's go back there first."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story08","chara":[{"id":102001,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"I didn't consider...","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"That it would be such a crisis,@that humanity would disappear..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"First, let's analyze the situation and think of a@solution."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"...I think Kagome's existence is one key."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"There is no doubt."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"Out of the memories of La Pucelle that we managed@to store in the Ark, there are only six volumes..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"And one of those volumes contains Kagome's@memories."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"When Torte came to visit,@the people around you"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"still remembered La Pucelle Jeanne's name, right?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":831700,"pos":2}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Yes... Iroha, Yachiyo, Ui, and Sakurako..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Ah, Felicia didn't seem to know though..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"There might be some common trait there."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"For example, they may all be"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"girls connected by causality with La Pucelle..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"charaBack"}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"And what about that pen?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"This mysterious magic pen...@[chara:402601:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:402601:motion_200][chara:402601:lipSynch_1]It couldn't possibly be unrelated!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/51158_kagome_magical_pencil.png","visible":"hide"}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"It belongs to a girl from the future who@records Magical Girls with her magic pen."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Among those records, there are many@related to La Pucelle Jeanne,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"which are in danger of disappearing..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Kagome's actions might be@helping protect the future"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"from the erosion of the world of the red moon."},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"[chara:402901:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story23","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"Yes, that's right."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"We were looking for a way to restore our world..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"And Kagome's continuous recording might be the@key."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"What do you mean?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50},{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"If Kagome Satori, a resident of the \"future\",@records Tart,"},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"then \"the past where Tart existed\" cannot be erased."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Moreover, that pen and notebook are protected by@some kind of magic..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"There's also Torte's existence."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Torte meeting Kagome couldn't have been a mere@coincidence."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Anyway, if we can help you continue to record@Tart's memories..."},{"chara":[{"id":402301}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Can we return the world to its original state?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"That's the plan, I believe."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Yes!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"There's one more thing I've noticed."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Elisa","textLeft":"What is it?"},{"chara":[{"id":831700,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"The identity of that red moon."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Huh...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Doesn't its red color look quite similar to the color@of the Ark?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"...Indeed, it does."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402901}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":831700,"pos":1}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"In each world, there's a unique \"color\"."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"When viewed through a certain type of magic,@things belonging to different worlds"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"are said to appear in different colors."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"If that red color is the true color of our original@world..."},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"Then that red moon might be the shadow of our@world"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"as seen from the world without La Pucelle."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831700}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome","textCenter":"Our world's...shadow?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"Yes, if the erosion is completed and our world@disappears,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Nicolas","textCenter":"that red moon might disappear too."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831700}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":200,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"We won't allow such a thing."},{"chara":[{"id":402301,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"That's right!"},{"chara":[{"id":402301}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"We will never let Tart's memories be erased!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402601},{"effect":"fadeout","id":402301}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":200,"pos":2,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Yes! Let's do our best!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"By the way...um...how do we return to the Ark?"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Shouldn't you...conduct an interview?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...with whom?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_11131.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":1,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameCenter":"Melissa & Elisa","textCenter":"..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"black","bgm":"stop","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeInTime":1.0},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"white","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"nameNarration":"","narration":"[textBlack:―Interview Record―@Melissa de Vignolles@Elisa Celjska]","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut","turnChangeOutTime":0.2},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":2,"posX":30}],"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"bgm":"bgm20_song10","nameNarration":"Melissa","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":80.0,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"If possible, I want to@  see Tart right away...@  That might be my true desire.\"]","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":402301,"motion":300}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"But it's something that@  can never be fulfilled...@  In that case, I thought that@  inheriting Tart's feelings would@  be the path for me to live.\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"That's why I will continue to@  fight from now on, until the@  peaceful world that Tart@  desired is realized.\"]"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"black","chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2,"posX":30}],"item":[{"iPhoneXScale":1.0,"path":"resource/scenario/img/51030_fishing_homura/51030_homura_dairy.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"bgFront"}],"narrationEffect":"out","turnChangeIn":"whiteIn"},{"nameNarration":"Elisa","narrationCoverOpacity":0.0,"narrationEffect":"in","narrationHAlignment":"left","narrationPosX":80.0,"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"For true salvation to come to Tart...@  That is the only thing I desire.\"]","turnChangeOut":"whiteOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":300}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"But Tart won't wish for her own@  salvation. Until the very last@  moment, she thought of others@  and died for the sake of others...\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"That's why I will keep on living@  to the fullest. When the time@  comes for me to leave this world,@  I want to face Tart with pride.\"]"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":200}],"progressNarration":"[textBlack:  \"And I want to be able to@  proudly report to her that I@  have done this much for the@  peace of Europe as well...\"]"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
